    slug: 'cognitive-load-distracted-driving-road-safety-decisions',
    title: 'The Invisible Burden: How Cognitive Load from Distracted Driving Impairs Your Road Safety Decisions',
    category: 'Road Safety',
    excerpt: 'Explore how the cognitive load of distracted driving creates an invisible burden, impairing critical decision-making and increasing crash risks. Understand the science behind it.',
