    slug: 'critical-cycling-helmet-fitting-mistakes-fix',
    title: '7 Critical Cycling Helmet Fitting Mistakes That Compromise Your Safety (And How to Fix Them)',
    category: 'Road Safety',
    excerpt: 'Discover the 7 most common cycling helmet fitting errors that secretly reduce protection. Learn expert tips to correct them and maximize your safety on every ride.',
    metaDescription: 'Discover the 7 most common cycling helmet fitting errors that secretly reduce protection. Learn expert tips to correct them and maximize your safety on every ride.',
